episodes.title: I Am Legion
episodes.plot: The newly-escaped Lex Luthor is given a membership test for Gorilla Grodd's expanded Secret Society.

episodes.title: Shadow of the Hawk
episodes.plot: Shayera is approached by an archaeologist who is convinced that he is the reincarnated husband of a previous incarnation of her.

episodes.title: Chaos at the Earth's Core
episodes.plot: Green Lantern, Stargirl, S.T.R.I.P.E. and Supergirl are drawn to the subterranean world of Skartaris to assist the Warlord, Travis Morgan.

episodes.title: To Another Shore
episodes.plot: Wonder Woman finds herself fighting a team from the Secret Society determined to steal the frozen body of the Viking Prince.

episodes.title: Flash and Substance
episodes.plot: A day in the life of Wally West aka The Flash. The day includes West at his day job, as a Criminal Lab tech, the dedication of the Flash Museum, and the attacks of four villians.

episodes.title: Dead Reckoning
episodes.plot: Deadman calls on Batman, Superman, and Wonder Woman to help him recover an orb containing the souls of a monastic order that was stolen by the Secret Society.

episodes.title: Patriot Act
episodes.plot: The paranoid General Eiling turns himself into a superstrong brute to kill Superman and only seven non-powered soldiers of the JL can deny him victory.

episodes.title: The Great Brain Robbery
episodes.plot: Lex Luthor and the Flash accidentally switch bodies.

episodes.title: Grudge Match
episodes.plot: Roulette enlists the ladies of the JLU in her new & improved all-girl gladiatorial arena.

episodes.title: Far from Home
episodes.plot: On her 21st birthday, Supergirl is transported to the 31st century along with Green Lantern and Green Arrow, to help the "Legion of Super-Heroes" combat "The Fatal Five". However, according to future sources, it is a mission from which she does not return.

episodes.title: Ancient History
episodes.plot: Hawkman returns with Shadow Thief and discovers the true nature of his relationship with Hawkgirl.

episodes.title: Alive!
episodes.plot: When Lex Luthor sends the Secret Society headquarters into outer space to find the remains of Brainiac, Grodd breaks free of his prison to lead a mutiny.

episodes.title: Destroyer
episodes.plot: The resurrected Darkseid leads his force on an all-out attack on Earth in revenge against Superman and the Justice League and Secret Society must join forces to stop him.
